claim.claim-text:
A server (132) comprising:
one or more processors (210);
memory (230);
a communication subsystem (220); and
a module executable by the one or more processors (210) to configure the one or more processors (210) to perform the method of any one of claims 1 to 9.

A method implemented by a processor (340) of an electronic device (301), the method comprising:
sending a request to a server (132) over a wireless network connection to download content from a third-party server (136);
receiving an authorization message from the server (132), the authorization message being generated based on applying one or more pre-determined rules (238) to the request, wherein the one or more pre-determined rules (238) are based on an estimate by the server (132) of wireless network traffic load;
determining that the authorization message permits a download session with the third-party server (136); and
initiating the download session directly with the third-party server (136).

An electronic device (301) comprising:
a processor (340);
memory (344);
a communication subsystem (311); and
a module executable by the processor (340) to configure the processor (340) to perform the method of claim 12.
